Enclosing class:
ConfigurationsPreferencePage
private class ConfigurationsPreferencePage.KiemIntegerPropertyInputField
extends java.lang.Object

Handles a Text input field with label and tooltip for one of the default KIEM properties.

The class also provides a save method to write the contents of the text field to the back end.
